data.description: Stunning 4-Bedroom Home in Gibsonton, Florida - Move-In Ready!    Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Gibsonton, Florida! This impeccable 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a split floor plan and a plethora of desirable features that make it a true gem. With a roof and HVAC system that is only 6 years old, a spacious open-concept layout, and modern amenities, this home is perfect for those seeking comfort and convenience.    Some of this homes Key Features include:     4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for families of all sizes.  The roof and HVAC system are only 6 years old, offering peace of mind and efficiency.  The large open-concept kitchen and living area create a welcoming and inclusive space for gatherings and entertaining.  The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting a large island with granite countertops and plenty of cabinets for storage.  Stainless steel refrigerator, range, microwave, dishwasher, and a brand new washer and dryer are included.  The master bedroom is a retreat on its own, featuring an en suite bathroom with dual sinks, a walk-in shower, and a spacious walk-in closet.  Step outside to the fully screened lanai and enjoy the serene view of nature provided by the mature trees in the conservation area - a tranquil oasis right in your backyard.  The vinyl privacy fence ensures your peaceful enjoyment of the outdoor space.  With 2,022 square feet, a 2-car garage, and a separate laundry room, functionality and storage are abundant.  This home is immaculately maintained and move-in ready now.  The Carriage Pointe community offers,     Recreation Facilities: Enjoy a range of recreational activities right at your doorstep. Whether you're a fitness enthusiast, a sports lover, or simply enjoy spending time outdoors, our community has something for everyone.  Large Community Swimming Pool: Dive into relaxation and beat the heat with our refreshing swimming pool. It's the perfect spot to unwind, socialize, or simply soak up the sun.  Tennis Courts: Showcase your skills on the tennis courts and engage in friendly matches with friends and neighbors. It's a great way to stay active and bond with the community.  Basketball Courts: Shoot some hoops and partake in friendly basketball games, fostering a sense of camaraderie and friendly competition among residents.  Large Ponds: Our scenic ponds add a touch of natural beauty to the neighborhood. Take a leisurely stroll around the ponds, enjoy the wildlife, or simply bask in the serenity they provide.  Proximity to Convenience:    Shopping Centers: Within a few miles, you'll find a variety of shopping centers, making it convenient to fulfill your retail needs, grocery shopping, dining, and more.  Interstate Access: Enjoy easy access to major highways, including the interstate, which makes commuting a breeze and opens up endless possibilities for exploration and adventure.    This captivating home in Gibsonton, Florida, is a true treasure that won't stay on the market for long. Its modern amenities, spacious layout, and stunning conservation area view make it a must-see for discerning buyers. Take advantage of this fantastic opportunity and make this house your forever home. Act now and embrace a life of comfort and convenience in this beautiful space!
